don't consider this a crime. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Clinton</ENAMEX>'s surrogates have exploited this paradox
by accusing <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Starr</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Republicans</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Congress</ENAMEX>, and conservative <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Clinton</ENAMEX> haters of
